QuestData.Title: More Than Expected
QuestData.Description: Ya definitely more den expected, mon. I'm sure dere's more important stuff we can be usin' ya talents on now. Ya don't need ta hang out with da newbloods no more.$B$BHead down to da village to da southeast and make yaself known. Lend a hand here and there and I'm sure ya make yer way up to sometin' more prestigious quick enough.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Vol'jin at Darkspear Hold.
QuestData.RewardText: Ya tha new recruit everyone's talkin' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.
